## Limitations
The findings presented are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives on personality change. The studies referenced primarily focus on Western populations, which may limit the generalizability of the results to other cultural contexts. Additionally, the complexity of personality and its interaction with environmental factors means that individual experiences of personality change can vary widely.

